    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dr Livesey vs Banana Cat? Chad vs Sanik? What the hell is this?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MEMOLOGY: War of Memes is just a new part of the legendary MEMOLOGY series of games, in which you have to build your own personal army of meme characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Distribute your budget, pay attention to the characters' characteristics, build your meme army and just enjoy this madness. We hope that you completed all parts of MEMOLOGY and become the best meme commander!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Single player and multiplayer for up to 4 people</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 5 different and unique locations for battles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 7 recognizable characters from memes </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- well-thought-out story campaign</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Adjustable battle speed</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Solid madness and unpredictability</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So which meme will win?</p>",
